their product but rather when it is delivered to a dealer therefore it is possible for the manufacturer to inflate sales numbers by requiring dealers to accept more inventory than desired in a practice called channel stuffing when demand softened following the unique  model year this news led to a dramatic decline in the stock price in april  alone the price of hog shares dropped from more than  to less than  immediately prior to this decline retiring ceo jeffrey bleustein profited  million on the exercise of employee stock options harleydavidson was named as a defendant in numerous class action suits filed by investors who claimed they were intentionally defrauded by harleydavidsons management and directors by january  the price of harleydavidson shares reached  problems with police touring models starting around  several police departments started reporting problems with high speed instability on the harleydavidson touring motorcycles a raleigh north carolina police officer charles paul was killed when his  police touring motorcycle crashed after reportedly experiencing a high speed wobble the california highway patrol conducted testing of the police touring motorcycles in  the chp test riders reported experiencing wobble or weave instability while operating the motorcycles on the test track  strike on february   upon the expiration of their union contract about  employees at harleydavidson incs largest manufacturing plant in york pennsylvania went on strike after failing to agree on wages and health benefits during the pendency of the strike the company refused to pay for any portion of the striking employees health care the day before the strike after the union voted against the proposed contract and to authorize the strike the company shut down all production at the plant the york facility employs more than  workers both union and nonunion harleydavidson announced on february   that it had reached a labor agreement with union workers at its largest manufacturin